{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "展梦白潜入帝王谷寻找萧飞雨之父，先在花园中与萧飞雨重逢，萧飞雨见他冷漠无情，伤心落泪。白袍妇人（萧飞雨的阿姨）现身与展梦白交手，驼背老人（六叔）及时制止，并透露是他将展梦白送入谷中。展梦白借故脱身，小兰暗中指引他避开消息机关。展梦白误入萧曼风的密室，萧曼风设下美人计试图戏弄他，展梦白反以其人之道还治其人之身，迫使萧曼风反被震慑。最终萧曼风被展梦白的胆识折服，同意带他前往其父闭关之处。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在那边，不知逃了没有？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下在此恭候。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "就是这臭小子，他擅入花园中来，还将小兰她们的兵刃……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你怎么来了？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "我来不得么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "谁说你来不得，我只是问问你。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "问什么？有什么好问的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不问就不问好么？我又……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "不问也不行。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "姑娘，这小子必定是得了疯疾，是以在这里颠三倒四，胡说八道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "滚开，谁要你多嘴？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你是不是有心事？无论什么事，都可以告诉我……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你说话呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "我的话要等见到你父亲时再说！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我爹爹？你要见他老人家做什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "自然有事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你要见他老人家也可以，只可惜……唉，只可惜他老人家正在坐关，什么人也见不得。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "你带我去他坐关之地，我自会唤他出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你教我做什么事我都可答应，就只这件事……我是万万不能答应的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "不答应我也偏偏要见他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我次次让你，你次次欺负我，你……你……你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "在下一介庸才，怎敢欺负萧宫主？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "展梦白，你以为……你以为我……我怕你么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "这里是萧宫主势力范围，怎会怕区区在下？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好，这里是我势力范围，我……我要……我要……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "萧宫主要动手么，好，在下奉陪。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "难怪你要跑来欺负我，原来你……你在别处学会了惊人的武功……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "萧宫主过奖了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你武功再强我也不怕你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "飞雨，我听花大姑说你这里来了嘉客，你怎地却同嘉客打了起来？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_bai_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "阿姨，我……我……好伤心……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "飞雨，乖，不要哭。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你真要伤她？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_bai_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "是又怎样？不是又怎样？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好极了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_bai_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "一齐住手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "老六，这不关你的事，退开去。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_bai_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "谁说不关我事，这孩子是我送来的，我岂能不管？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "你送来的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "六叔，你认得他么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "世上难道只有你一人认得他么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小伙子，老夫将你送来，本是要你来陪陪我这二侄女的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "叫他来陪飞雨？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "她脾气虽坏，但心肠却软，是以我叫你放大胆子说话，她必定不会不理你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "但你的胆也未免太大了些，怎么在帝王谷中，也敢胡乱找人打架？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "无论何时何地，只要有人欺侮于我，想要与我动手，本人都万万不会退缩的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好，少年人如此心性，也不为过，但老夫却要问一句……你武功是谁传授于你的？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "你管不着。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你既然认得飞雨，老夫也……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "谁认得她。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你……你好！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好小子，你竟敢欺负萧家的人，老夫教你尝尝大卸八块的滋味。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "看在你带路的分上，我让你三招。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好小子，你敢让老夫三招？武林中人见到老夫一怒，莫不骇得胆颤心惊，你凭什么不怕？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "你有四只手么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "放屁，谁说我有四只手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "你我俱是两只手，我为何要怕你？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好小子，你真有种，老夫倒要交交你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "我自然有种，我连闭起眼睛，头顶着地，向前连走二十步都敢一试，还怕别的什么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "这种玩意儿连三尺幼童都敢试上一试，难道也是稀罕危险之事么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "你不敢也就算了，何必空言吓人，这件事看来轻易，其实……嘿嘿，却危险得很。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你小子诡计多端，必定有什么阴谋，老夫才不上当哩！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你以为我当真不敢么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "嘿嘿……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小子，你看着，一，二……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小子，你输……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "公子……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lan",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lan",
      "text": "我要去寻你家谷主的闭关之地。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "呀，你……你寻着了，他老人家也不会见你的，而且……说不定还会有杀身之祸。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "求求你，不要去吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lan",
      "text": "你放心，我身上带有别人给你谷主的信物，去了他必定会见我的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你既有信物，若是拿出来，他们就自然会带你去了，何必多费这么多事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lan",
      "text": "有许多事，你不会懂的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不，我懂，我小时只听人说故事，韩信去见刘邦时，也不肯将张良的信物拿出来，你……你就和韩信一样，是为了要争一口英雄之气，是么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lan",
      "text": "淮阴侯一代英雄，我怎比得上他？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不，你们都是一样。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "帝王谷里，看守的人不多，但路上却处处都有消息。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你只要不踩在石路上，一直走，走到一座最好看的房子，就是……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lan",
      "text": "那就是你家谷主的坐关之地了么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lan",
      "text": "你何必将如此机密告诉我？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你是英雄，我自然要帮你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lan",
      "text": "你……唉，多谢了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你快走吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "只要你记着我，以后总会见面的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lan",
      "text": "小兰，你一直守在这里，可曾看到那少年出去么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lan",
      "speaker_name": "小兰",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "没有呀！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子，老夫在这儿守着你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "展梦白，你一入谷，我就知道你会来找我的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "你是萧曼风么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不是我是谁呀？你在外面坐坐，我早已替你准备好了酒菜，等一会我就出来陪你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "谁要你陪？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你呀，你这个人，我叫你不要进来，你偏偏不听，看等一会我不告诉二妹才怪。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "这铜镜乃是千年风磨铜所制，坚逾精钢，你功力再深十倍，也毁不了它的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "你到底要怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我到底要怎样么？……这就要看你了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "这密室乃是我精心所制，世上除了我谁也开不了，你若打死我，你也出不去了，那时……那时你便要陪我一齐死在这里，直到千百年后，人们发现我俩的尸身，你知道他们会怎么想？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "他们必定要以为我们是一对殉情而死的鸳鸯情侣，我们不是更冤枉么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你叹什么气呀？我们还没有死哩！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "我与你无冤无仇，你何苦如此害人？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "哎呀，谁害你呀！我请你吃菜，请你喝酒，自己还陪着你，这难道是害你么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "来呀！你怕什么？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "你以为我不敢吃么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你难道不怕这酒菜中有穿肠毒药，吃了立刻会死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "死了也做个饱死鬼。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你难道不怕这酒菜中有媚药，你吃了后就会……就会……就会怎样，你也该知道。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "这酒菜中若真有媚药，我吃了后只有你应该害怕才是，我怕什么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "喂，我笑什么？你可知道？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "哦，你在笑么，我不知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我笑你还蒙在鼓里，一点也不知道，老实告诉你……这酒菜中的毒药，人吃了虽不会死，但全身立刻半分气力也没有了，那时……那时我就要零零碎碎地折磨你，虐待你，叫你吃尽苦处，再慢慢死去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "能吃到这种毒药，也算我口福不错，再死在你这样的美人手上，也算死得不冤了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你吃完了么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "酒足饭饱了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你觉得怎样？你的手是否已酸了？你的关节是否麻木了？你若要命，快跪下求饶。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "我的手也不酸，身子也不麻，我只觉舒服极了，平生都没有如此舒服过。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "死到临头，还要嘴硬么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "死了也好做个风流鬼。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "我要做什么，你难道不知道么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你……你……你敢走过来一步？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "你答应我么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你……你……你敢碰我一碰。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "来，不要怕，没有人会看见的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "无……无耻的奴才，你……你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "我无耻？这是你自己要的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "求求你，不要……不要……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "有……有人来了，快……快放开。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "不要紧，这密室除了你之外，谁也打不开的，这话不是你自己说的么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "求求你，只要你放开我，我什么都答应。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "好，你既然坚决不肯，唉！只要你将我带到你爹爹坐关之地，我就放了你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "这件事我实在没办法，唉……冤家，我就给了你吧……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "色鬼，你怎么也怕了？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你若再装得像些，我就信了，只可惜你不是色鬼，装也装不像的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "谁说我不是色鬼，我……我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你方才抱我时只敢抱我的肩头，我就知道你是在演戏了，我见的色鬼多了，哪有这么斯文的？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "把戏揭穿了，你现在要怎么样？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "我只觉冤得很。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不要叹气，走，我带你去爹爹的坐关之地。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "你……你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你是我生平所遇第一个能令我手足失措的男人，我不但有些喜欢你，也有些佩服你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "你的话可是真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 724
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "这一次我不但放开你，还依你的话将你送去，但下一次你碰到我时，我还是要和你斗一斗的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "text": "你纵带我去，我也不会感激你，你……可知道我是为什么来的？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_man_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧曼风",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我既不要你感激我，也不管你是为什么来的，只要是我情愿做的事，我什么都不管。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 736
    }
